# ==============================
# FacultyWare — Project Specific
# ==============================

# Dokumentasi internal AI (jangan push ke repo)
CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md

# Script migrasi lokal (sudah tidak dipakai, hanya referensi)
scripts/migrate_categories.js

# File foto upload oleh user (jangan push)
# CATATAN DEPLOY: filesystem Railway bersifat ephemeral — foto upload akan hilang saat
# redeploy. Untuk produksi gunakan object storage (mis. S3) atau volume persisten Railway.
public/uploads/equipment/*
# Tapi tetap track folder-nya agar ada saat clone
!public/uploads/equipment/.gitkeep

